            h1 Android
            h2 MK802 Mini PC
            h3 Running Android 4.0, the MK802 Allwinner A10 Mini PC is designed for versatility and convenience.  The tiny 200 gram PC can plug directly into any HDMI output for an on the go media player, internet browser, game machine or for general use.
